Package: openaps-base
Version: __OPENAPS_VERSION__
Architecture: all
Maintainer: OpenAPS <bdbruin@gmail.com>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends:
Description: OpenAPS base layout — release key, rollback CLI, settings provisioning.
 Ships /etc/openaps/release.pub (the OTA release-signing public key) and
 /usr/bin/openaps-rollback. Its postinst provisions
 /etc/inv-driver/settings.json from /etc/yuneng/*.conf when absent. Every
 OpenAPS service package depends on this one.
